Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.54,0:00:58.69,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}I've been ignoring everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.69,0:01:00.99,EN-op,,0,0,0,,I've been wandering around
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.39,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I've been deceived everything. At that time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.75,0:01:10.44,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Then you appeared in front of me. You ignited my pale heart
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.46,0:01:14.74,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}We've been looking for each other from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.76,0:01:15.95,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Save you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.10,0:01:21.54,JP-op,,0,0,0,,際限ない犠牲を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.02,0:01:26.92,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}朦朧とした理想を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.69,0:01:30.67,JP-op,,0,0,0,,もう無駄にしないようにと
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.67,0:01:35.29,JP-op,,0,0,0,,悲しみを切り刻んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.99,0:01:38.31,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.54,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.56,0:01:45.73,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Just now. Chip at your heart. We just fight for freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.86,0:01:50.44,JP-op,,0,0,0,,奪い合って　汚し合って
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.44,0:01:54.63,JP-op,,0,0,0,,それでも守りたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.03,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.03,0:02:00.49,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.50,0:02:05.00,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}We don't want to go through that again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.00,0:02:10.57,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}時は満ちた　始まりの鐘が鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.53,0:02:17.60,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Get away from me
