Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:29.22,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Would I still have a chance for us to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:35.51,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:42.99,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}If I decide to burn instead of fading out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:46.99,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}I still would like the chance for us to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:54.37,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:58.89,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(400,400)}If we can be found, we sure can get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:03.33,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(200,400)}Through all the madness of falling in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:10.58,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(200,400)}If we're truly lost, I don't want to be found here dying alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.86,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(400,0)}The stain of RED that colors the pavement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:16.91,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}The stain of RED that colors the pavement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.91,0:22:20.87,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Painted with blood of somebody you love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.17,0:22:23.45,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)}Is this sacrifice for the broken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:25.73,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(0,400)}Is this sacrifice for the broken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.45,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(400,0)}Losing the purest of what's in your heart
